name: Tinyworlds

# These rings aren’t normal rings 
![blue dream](https://pp.vk.me/c638417/v638417969/3dad/RrujJ6uzWLI.jpg)

## These rings contain secret worlds

They’re all handmade using fresh wood, jewelry resin, and beeswax, and no two rings are the same which means that the little world you’ll carry on your finger is unique only to you.
We’ve crafted some handsome templates for you to use. Go ahead and click 'Continue to layouts' to browse through them. You can easily go back to edit your page before publishing. After publishing your page, you can revisit the page generator and switch to another theme. Your Page content will be preserved.
